    "Background": {
      "text": "Polio\n-like illness, subset of\ntransverse myelitis\nMore common in children\nLikely caused by:\nEnterovirus\n, particularly\nEnterovirus D68\n,\npoliovirus\nWest nile virus\nAdenovirus",
