          "text": "corticosteroids",
          "url": "https://wikem.org/wiki/Corticosteroids"
        },
        {
          "text": "IVIG",
          "url": "https://wikem.org/wiki/IVIG"
        }
      ]
    },
    "Disposition": {
      "text": "Admit\nConsider ICU admission for:\nRespiratory muscle weakness\nBulbar weakness causing impaired airway protection\nAltered mental status\nAutonomic instability\nCervical lesion on MRI\nRapidly progressive course",
